<h1>Terms &amp; Conditions</h1>

<div class="box">
  <p><strong>TCC Sentinel SMS Program</strong> — an internal application monitoring alert service operated by The Children's Center, Inc. The sole recipient is the business owner. Messages are transactional operational alerts, not marketing.</p>
